                          <p style={{ paddingLeft: "30px" }}><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>9.1 Each Party (“Indemnifying Party”) agrees to indemnify, defend and hold harmless the other Party</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>including its parent</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>subsidiaries, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>affiliates </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>and each of their respective officers</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>directors, agents, employees, members</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>Clients and its Representatives (“Indemnified Party”) from and against any third­ party </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>claim</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>action, or </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>liability </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>(including damages, costs</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>, </span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>expenses, and reasonable attorneys’ fees) that may arise against the Indemnified Party as the result of</span><span style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>:</span></p>
