                            <li style={{ fontWeight: "400" }}>t<span style={{ fontSize: "14px" }}>he misappropriation </span><span style={{ fontSize: "14px" }}>or misuse of the Indemnified Party’s Confidential Information by the Indemnifying Party.</span></li>
